# Codebase Structure

## Workspaces

The project is organized into several workspaces:

### app

Frontend application:
- `app/src` - Main application source
- `app/app` - Application-specific code
- `app/index.ts` - Entry point
- `app/elm.json` - Dependencies

### package

Core library for motorsport data analysis:
- `package/src/Motorsport` - Domain models
- `package/src/DataView.elm` - Visualization components
- `package/tests` - Unit tests

### cli

Command-line tools for data processing:
- `cli/src` - CLI implementations
- `cli/benchmark` - Performance benchmarks
- `cli/fixture` - Test fixtures

### review

Elm Review configuration:
- `review/src` - Custom review rules

## Configuration Files

- `package.json` - Root package config and workspaces
- `biome.json` - JS/TS linting
- `.devcontainer` - Dev container config
- `.vscode` - Editor settings

## Build System

The project uses npm workspaces to manage the different components.
